// console.log("i can see you"); var webinarForm = document.querySelector(".book-session-form"); var webinarDetails = document.querySelectorAll(".form-control"); var webinarFormName = document.querySelector("h1"); var webinarFormDay = document.getElementById("SelectedDate"); function getTimeSlotValue(){ var radios = document.querySelector("input[name=choose-time]:checked").value; radioValue = radios; console.log(radioValue); return radioValue; } webinarForm.addEventListener("submit", (e)=>{ e.preventDefault(); const firstName = webinarDetails[0].value; const email = webinarDetails[1].value; const phone = webinarDetails[2].value; const query = webinarDetails[3].value; const date = webinarFormDay.innerText; const exactTime = getTimeSlotValue();; const webinarName = webinarFormName.innerText; sendEmail(firstName, email, phone, query, webinarName, date, exactTime); webinarForm.reset(); }) var sendEmail = (firstname, email, phone, query, formName, date, time) =>{ // console.log(name, email, password); Email.send({ Host : "smtp.innovativewebservice.com", Username : "info@innovativewebservice.com", Password : "Iws@2020", To : 'info@innovativewebservice.com', From : "info@innovativewebservice.com", Subject : `New Submission from ${formName} Form`, Body : `

Dear Active Bug Rep,

We've got new learning interest from ${firstname}.
Below are the details of the client.

Firstname: ${firstname}

Email: ${email}

Preferred Time: ${date}

Time Slot: ${time}

Phone: ${phone}

Message/Query: ${query}
 
 

Thank you, Innovative Web Service
`, }).then( message => alert("Form Submission Successfull!") ); }
